Running instructions:

1. Use make to build executable
   $ make clean
   $ make a4

2. Run program N times as:
      $ ./p4 N b c F B P S T
 
   where:
       N Number of peer nodes
       b gossip parameter
       c gossip parameter
       F number of seconds after which a node is considered dead
       B number of bad nodes that should fail
       P number of seconds to wait between failures
       S the see of the random number generator
       T the total number of seconds to run

********************************************************************************
Behaviour of gossip protocol under various test cases:

We will keep following as base values for all parameters and modify few of them
for each test case to show different behaviour.




Test case 1.  
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

N  b c  F  B P S T
10 4 30 10 4 5 1 30

  9        8        7        6       5        4         3       2        1        0

 OK    |  FAIL  |  FAIL  |  OK    |  OK    |  OK    |  FAIL  |  OK    |  FAIL  |  OK
 0 28  |  0 14  |  0 8   |  0 29  |  0 28  |  0 29  |  0 5   |  0 29  |  0 19  |  1 20
 1 20  |  1 14  |  1 9   |  1 20  |  1 20  |  1 20  |  1 5   |  1 20  |  2 19  |  2 29
 2 29  |  2 14  |  2 9   |  2 29  |  2 29  |  2 29  |  2 4   |  3 5   |  3 5   |  3 5
 3 5   |  3 5   |  3 5   |  3 5   |  3 5   |  3 5   |  4 5   |  4 29  |  4 19  |  4 29
 4 29  |  4 15  |  4 10  |  4 29  |  4 29  |  5 29  |  5 4   |  5 29  |  5 18  |  5 29
 5 29  |  5 14  |  5 9   |  5 29  |  6 29  |  6 29  |  6 4   |  6 29  |  6 19  |  6 29
 6 29  |  6 14  |  6 9   |  7 10  |  7 10  |  7 10  |  7 5   |  7 10  |  7 10  |  7 10
 7 10  |  7 10  |  8 9   |  8 15  |  8 15  |  8 15  |  8 5   |  8 15  |  8 15  |  8 15
 8 15  |  9 14  |  9 9   |  9 29  |  9 29  |  9 29  |  9 4   |  9 29  |  9 19  |  9 29

We regard this as base testcase for analysis. We will be comparing result of this testcase to other testcases output.
Nodes failed are 1(at heartbeat 20),3(5),7(10),8(15)
Due to high value of 'b' and 'c' each node is getting information of nodes failed. 


Test case 2 (set b = 1)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
N  b c  F  B P S T
10 1 30 10 4 5 1 30

  9        8        7        6       5        4         3       2        1        0

 OK    |  FAIL  |  FAIL  |  OK    |  OK    |  OK    |  FAIL  |  OK    |  FAIL  |  OK
