 8 15  |  9 13  |  9 5   |  9 29  |  9 29  |  9 25  |  9 3   |  9 27  |  9 20  |  9 25

Since 'b' is number of neighbors to send heartbeat and neighborlist, therefore there will be higher degree of 
seperation between nodes.

Low value of 'b' causes some nodes to have very old heartbeat values and those nodes might be considered dead 
depending on value of F.


