 8 14  |  9 14  |  9 9   |  9 29  |  9 29  |  9 9   |  9 4   |  9 7   |  9 18  |  9 8

'c' is parameter to denote time limit for  sending neighbor list. For values of 'c' we can observe neighbor list
is not shared and due to parameter 'F' nodes that do not send heartbeat directly will be considered dead after 'F' seconds.
